reviewText: This is real CTS training. I don't know if I have time right now for all this information, but it is indeed very cool.
The whole collection for this price is a good deal. It is a great tactical set. I know the method and this DVD is quality material.

I would like to recommend this Israeli Counter Terror Warfare DVDs Collection to
anyone who want to learn about real Israeli Counter Terror Warfare Methods and Tactics.
This DVD set allows you to understand the principles
and concepts of the Israeli Counter Terror Warfare.
This is the best DVD on the market!
I have seen all the DVDs and they are all great, each better then the next. Especially if you are familiar with the Israeli system. this is cool because you save some money by ordering all at once
